ic\b0 \highlight\uc2  confidence in Indonesian businesses. \par \par \uc2  Despite the registration of 600 firms for the fair last year, only 200 companies took part, causing substantial financial losses to JITC. \par \par \uc2  According to a local government \b \highlight22\uc2 regulation\b0 \highlight\uc2  issued in 1991, the privately run JITC is the only organization with the right to hold the Jakarta Fair. \par \par \uc2  But this year, the fair will be held jointly by JITC, PT Debindo and the state-run Jakarta Fair Foundation. \par \par \uc2  Sources said JITC earlier refused sole responsibility for the fair, because of the losses sustained last year. (04) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 1999 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010906dv7h00b7z\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
