\par\par \b \uc2  Rupiah dip not due to  \highlight22\uc2 interest rates \highlight\uc2  - BI. \b0\par\par\uc2 487 \uc2 words\par \uc2 28 July 1999\par \uc2 Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  9 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 1999 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  JAKARTA (JP): \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  Governor Sjahril Sabirin said on Tuesday the weakening of the rupiah was not caused by declining domestic \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2 , but rather demand for U.S. dollars. \par \par \uc2  He said that although nominal \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  had fallen over the past few months, real \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  were still high. \par \par \uc2  "(The weakening of the rupiah) is not because of the interest rate drop," Sjahril said on the sidelines of a seminar on the Year 2000 problem. \par \par \uc2  The rupiah closed unchanged at Rp 6,980 to the dollar on Tuesday. \par \par \uc2  Dealers said the market was bullish on the dollar, but \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  and state banks appeared to intervene every time the dollar tried to strengthen past the Rp 7,000 level. \par \par \uc2  The local currency has weakened over the past week, falling from Rp 6,707 to its current level. \par \par \uc2  Some traders said declining domestic \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2  and increasing political \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  over the upcoming November presidential election were the primary factors behind the weakening of the rupiah. \par \par \uc2  "I think a weakening of one or two days is a normal thing. There's also a real need for the U.S. dollar right now," Sjahril said without elaborating. \par \par \uc2  Some economists said dollar demand would increase as more companies reached debt restructuring deals with their foreign creditors. \par \par \uc2  "A restructuring deal means companies still have to repay their foreign debts and some people think the dollar has been quite cheap lately," said an economist at a securities firm. \par \par \uc2  Sjahril also dismissed suggestions the rupiah weakened because of market jitters caused by domestic political developments. \par \par \uc2  The \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  has allowed its benchmark interest rate to decline on the back of lower inflation. \par \par \uc2  The interest rate on \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2 's one-month SBI promissory note is now at 14.57 percent, compared to more than 35 percent earlier this year. \par \par \uc2  Sjahril said the benchmark interest rate could continue to fall as long as inflation remained low. \par \par \uc2  "Inflation in July may still be negative," he said. \par \par \uc2  The \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  expects the benchmark interest rate to drop to below 12 percent by the end of this year, which would lead to a further decline in bank lending rates. A decline in lending rates would allow the real sector to easier obtain bank financing. \par \par \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  expects inflation this year to be slightly higher than 6 percent. \par \par \uc2  The \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  has enjoyed deflation for four months in a row beginning in March. \par \par \uc2  At the height of the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  crisis last year, the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  suffered hyperinflation of more than 77 percent. \par \par \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  officials earlier said the benchmark interest rate could fall below 10 percent by the end of this year if inflation was capped at below 6 percent. \par \par \uc2  "But this may not be possible," \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2 's Miranda Goeltom recently said. \par \par \uc2  She said inflation could soar in December during the traditional festive season. (rei/cst) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 1999 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010906dv7s0044a\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
