\par\par \b \uc2  News Focus - CGI MEETS NEW GOVERNMENT AND NEW ATMOSPHERE. \b0\par\par\uc2 641 \uc2 words\par \uc2 2 February 2000\par \uc2 ANTARA - The Indonesian National News Agency\par \uc2 ANTARA\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2000 Asia Pulse Pte Limited. Asia Pulse gives no warranty or guarantee as to the accuracy of the information, Asia Pulse shall not be liable for errors or omissions in, or delays or interruptions to or cessation of delivery of, the data through its negligence or otherwise.\par \par \uc2  By: Ramdani Sirait \par \par \uc2  Jakarta, Feb 2 (antara) - Donor countries and international financial institutions grouped in the Consultative Group on Indonesia (CGI) ended its ninth meeting here Wednesday. \par \par \uc2  In the first ever meeting held in Jakarta, the capital of Indonesia, donors did not only meet the new government which was democratically elected, but it also found a new atmosphere during the two-day meeting held behind closed door. \par \par \uc2  "The donors were suprised with the government's explanation on measures to create good governance," Coordinating Minister for \b \highlight22\uc2 Economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , Finance and Industry Kwik Kian Gie said at a press conference. \par \par \uc2  The government, according to Kwik, pledged to combat practices of \par \par \uc2  corruption, collusion and nepotism, better known here as KKN, in the country. \par \par \uc2  The international community welcomed the government's willingness to \par \par \uc2  eliminate KKN. \par \par \uc2  "CGI plans to give technical assistance to Indonesia in combatting \par \par \uc2  corruption," World Bank Vice President Jean-Michel Severino who chaired the \par \par \uc2  meeting told the press. \par \par \uc2  For the first time also, some local non-governmental organizations have been \par \par \uc2  invited to the meeting and expressed their view on a plan of a new loan package \par \par \uc2  for Indonesia. \par \par \uc2  Outside the \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  building, the venue of the meeting, some 1,000 \par \par \uc2  people demonstrated demanding the CGI to stop giving loans to Indonesia. \par \par \uc2  Another thing that surprised the CGI was that the Indonesian government \par \par \uc2  proposed a smaller loan compared to the latest one. \par \par \uc2  Finance Minister Bambang Sudibyo who also attended the meeting said the \par \par \uc2  Indonesian government under President Abdurrahman Wahid has decided to \par \par \uc2  streamline the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  "That's why we didn't ask for a bigger loan from the CGI," he reiterated. \par \par \uc2  International confidence \par \par \uc2  Many sides were very surprised with the amount of the new loan package from \par \par \uc2  CGI which amounts to only US$4.7 billion, especially amid the \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainties\b0 \highlight\par \par \uc2  gripping the country until now. \par \par \uc2  The plan on setting up an international tribunal to try Indonesian generals \par \par \uc2  allegedly involved in the unrests in East Timor that had been proposed by the United Nations Commission on Human Rights (UNCHR) to UN Secretary General Kofi Annan, has created fear for a coup in the country. \par \par \uc2  But the CGI did not appear to be influenced by such rumours. \par \par \uc2  "The is a new sense of optimism that Indonesia can indeed resume the path of real development and yet, events in the past six months have shown us that stability is fragile and that optimism can quickly fade," Severino said in response to newsmen's questions on the country's \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertain\b0 \highlight\uc2  situation. \par \par \uc2  The amount of the loan Indonesia received from the CGI this year was lower \par \par \uc2  than last year's US$5.9 billion provided in Paris, French. \par \par \uc2  Japan, as usual, provided the biggest loan in the package (US$1.56 billion), \par \par \uc2  while the World Bank, which heads the CGI, pledged US$1.5 billion. \par \par \uc2  The countries grouped in the CGI are Australia, Austria, the Nehterlands, \par \par \uc2  Belgium, Canada, Denmark, Finland, French, Germany, Italy, Japan, Korea, New \par \par \uc2  Zealand, Norway, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, the U.K. and the United States. \par \par \uc2  While the member international agencies are the World Bank, the Asian \par \par \uc2  Development Bank, the United Nations, the European Union, IFAD, the International Finance Institution, Saudi Fund, Kuwait Fund, the International Development Bank and the Nordic International Bank. \par \par \uc2  CGI was formed in the late 1980s replacing the Inter-Governmental Group on \par \par \uc2  Indonesia (IGGI) led by the Netherlands. \par \par \uc2  Then President Soeharto urged Indonesia to withdraw from the group after \par \par \uc2  Dutch \b \highlight22\uc2 Economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  Minister J.P. Pronk alleged that his administration has mismanaged the group's fund. \par \par \uc2  (c) 2000 Asia Pulse Pte Limited. \par \par \uc2  Asia Pulse gives no warranty or guarantee as to the accuracy of the information, Asia Pulse shall not be liable for errors or omissions in, or delays or interruptions to or cessation of delivery of, the data through its negligence or otherwise. \par \par \uc2 Document antara0020010804dw22002n4\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
